{"tid":1890470,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"悲報》公主號包機會澳洲 遭驗2例確診","createTime":"2020-02-21T08:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T15:22:06.000Z","uid":168564,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3629154bd80223aee6310f44f04353afd3ea8335","tid":1890470,"uid":168564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:17:56.000Z","msg":"爆發新冠肺炎群聚感染的鑽石公主號，船上最後一批旅客今（21）日全部下船。先前離開的兩名澳洲人，<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然下船時檢測病毒為陰性，卻在返回澳洲後，先後被驗出武漢肺炎病毒陽性確診</span>。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲衛生部官員說，對這項結果並不意外，因為檢驗作業進行同時，病毒還持續在船上傳播。<br />\n<br />\n鑽石公主號上160多名澳洲乘客，回國後都被送到澳洲本土北方的熱帶海外領地，進行14天隔離。<br />\n<br />\n哈哈哈，政府要接中國武漢香港人返嚟<br />\n到時大家一鑊熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51044725b34396de34019b0db43a7e14b3fe280a","tid":1890470,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:20:45.000Z","msg":"我都唔意外<br />\n所以都預香港包機實有人中招再密閉環境瘋傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04354bca929766130bb519b53dff23e08b54d1b5","tid":1890470,"uid":167289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:21:45.000Z","msg":"日本已經放晒出去食壽司了"},{"pid":"09e6eb0f758f867709c3872847660fbfb47a6cf8","tid":1890470,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca1c0333512010ede9a9fb0e78d16e499403f29","tid":1890470,"uid":174502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:43:39.000Z","msg":"點解澳洲會冇事"},{"pid":"e72f503f97ac08cc5361a72147e3f628f1ed64f1","tid":1890470,"uid":156618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ca1c0333512010ede9a9fb0e78d16e499403f29","tid":1890470,"uid":174502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:43:39.000Z","msg":"點解澳洲會冇事"},